4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge who aspire to become cybersecurity specialists. The program spans 16 weeks and includes 3 live online classes per week, accommodating up to 16 participants. Students will gain foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, alongside advanced topics such as cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. The course focuses on data loss prevention and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, students receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. Courses are available in English and Spanish. More information can be found at https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop